text: right Jānis Lagzdiņš (born June 15, 1952, Liepāja) is a Latvian politician.www.cvk.lv He is a Deputy of the Saeima and a member of the People's Party. ==References== Category:1952 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Liepāja Category:Popular Front of Latvia politicians Category:Latvian Way politicians Category:People's Party (Latvia) politicians Category:Deputies of the Supreme Council of the Republic of Latvia Category:Deputies of the 5th Saeima Category:Deputies of the 6th Saeima Category:Deputies of the 7th Saeima Category:Deputies of the 8th Saeima Category:Deputies of the 9th Saeima
